Script contains the following features (Made specifically for Roblox) 

● WalkSpeed (Customization 0 - 100+)
● Fly (Cusomization 0 - 100)
- FlySpeed is based on WalkSpeed
- 0 disables fly feature
● HipHeight 
- (Customization 0.5 - 20) Above 20 wont work & Zero = impractical
● Teleport
- Toggle enables teleport click (Left Click or Right Click)
● ESP
- ESP @Username
- Distance ESP (Studs)
- ESP Player (Green/Blue/Red)
ESP also works in MM2, Allows player to identify whether they are Innocent, Sheriff or Murderer without dying.
ESP works smoothly in small servers but may have some trouble in regular/big sized servers (6 - 12) Players so disabling and reenabling from time to time will help.
This script is clean and contains no item stealers.
Please use responsibly and don't bully others.
